N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 135.10 - Certificates of approval for cash compensation

State Regulations

The Director of the Budget shall file certificates of
approval for cash compensation for scheduled overtime with the Department of

Audit and Control, the Department of Civil Service, the Senate Finance

Committee and the Assembly Ways and Means Committee. Notes
